{"tid":424218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星如揀渣對手刷排名？ 教練︰網民淨係識google","createTime":"2017-10-04T13:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T14:00:59.000Z","uid":78546,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"afe3cfc8038e624a1f9564d86a6c3dbb81a9d58e","tid":424218,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171004&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=57285833&amp;ref=tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171004%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D57285833%26ref%3Dtw&d=yxM3Qndy4bKMQGtp966Fz6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=ef786d30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171004%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D57285833%26ref%3Dtw&h=13f1689f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171004&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=57285833&amp;ref=tw</a><br />\n<br />\n「有人話阿Rex揾啲對手刷排名，好似上一場對手向井寛史係咪一個渣嘅拳手呢？如果first 3% of the world係渣嘅話，I don't know！」<br />\n<br />\n「神奇小子」曹星如（Rex）將於10月7日主場迎戰前世界拳擊協會（WBA）超蠅量級世界冠軍、日本拳手河野公平，力爭22連勝。雖然Rex嘅打不死精神振奮咗唔少香港人，但一直以嚟亦有聲音批評Rex專揀弱對手刷排名。作為一直同Rex並肩作戰嘅前經理人﹑以及香港拳擊推廣人兼總教練劉志遠（Jay）今次接受蘋果訪問，都把握機會回應指控。<br />\n<br />\nJay 表示：「BoxRec只不過係義務機構去做呢啲排名，你刷到第一都唔會有一個仙。佢哋（網民）淨係識去google，但係啲排名就分得好亂，佢哋唔知道BoxRec嘅排名，同埋世界組織嘅排名嘅分別。」此外，佢又認為 Rex之所以咁努力去練習比賽，絕對唔係為咗個光環：「一個運動員係咪為咗個光環去爭取勝利？我哋每一場比賽得到嘅喜悅唔係因為勝利，而係喺中間付出過嘅努力。答案唔一定係贏或者輸，而係可以證明到我哋出咗100%嘅力，盡全力去做到一件事。」<br />\n<br />\n回應種種批評，Jay 都難忍激動，但當講到由當初冇乜人睇 Rex比賽蝕錢收場，直到對上一次坐爆8000人， Jay 終於笑番晒，仲由心講出一句「 我哋全部都好proud of 阿Rex！」<br />\n<br />\n記者：植詠珊(Cathy)<br />\n剪接﹑編審﹑導演：Roy Leung@天馬座<br />\n攝影：廖達燊﹑Kaman"},{"pid":"6df4854497ee386754bc3d77c4bc5b21fb2dd3e2","tid":424218,"uid":145365,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"4bbae825857bd10d9e07b0688787251ef651a06b","tid":424218,"uid":1672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"佢咪又係靠星如賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9b84c8c0b7139db44465f6d5e0d33a3948d786","tid":424218,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"佢d對手google唔到...."},{"pid":"56752f31c34ed37e77c63090a113fc40c8fceade","tid":424218,"uid":51129,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"first 3% of the world都好吹？<br />\n喂水晶宮都first 3% of the world啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e033f8dce99d2ef54da8ecf76e596ec5794c260f","tid":424218,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>first 3% of the world都好吹？<br />\n喂水晶宮都first 3% of the world啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔揀對手咁點解唔同世界第一既打呢"},{"pid":"55b6edbb0435c9f882847ed5f40a68980afe1a28","tid":424218,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>first 3% of the world都好吹？<br />\n喂水晶宮都first 3% of the world啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔揀對手咁點解唔同世界第一既打呢</blockquote><br />\n依家係邀請埋都拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a3983d5b74e09b9bd326fede15c946e0151eb","tid":424218,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢d對手google唔到....</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}